VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (assert|eval)\s*\(\s*(\$_(GET|POST|REQUEST)|\$\{?(?:_[a-zA-Z0-9_]+|[a-zA-Z_\x7f-\xff][a-zA-Z0-9_\x7f-\xff]*)\}?)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:validate|allowlist|trusted|intval|is_int|is_numeric && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects usage of assert() and eval() with potentially untrusted inputs, leading to code injection vulnerabilities.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure Code Execution: assert() and eval().
